column5: With the water being gin clear and forecast for for blue bird skies trout fishing was out of the question.  So..............  we went and hunted Walleyes!!!  Started off with a new PB   Then beat it a half hour later    We boated a good number of smallies too!! Was a great morning!  Tight Lines Luke
Good on ya Luke! Them's fine looking walleyes. Congrats and thanks for the report.
I have Lemon pepper and butter
Twocoda. There on the BBQ as we speak
Awesome fish.  Never caught a Lake-O walleye that wasn't SUPER fat.
Nice! Hope you enjoy that sweet meat!
nice shooting there Luke, must 've had some Cool Hands
Hands were just fine. I never wear gloves.....  I must be slow. That took me a minute to catch the joke lol
"What we have here is a failure to communicate."
Great eyes Luke.  They're just pure chunk.
Congrats on the PB!!! Nice specimens.
